2026-03-16 00:36:25,569 - user_id=web question=how can i invest in land in indonesia ? path=rag_during_flow score=None answer=Foreigners can invest in land in Indonesia through a PT PMA company. The company must be established with a minimum of 60% foreign ownership. The remaining 40% can be owned by an Indonesian partner.
